{"ID":"20250919151530-t59ra5z","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20250919151530-t59ra5z","title":"03 自我一致性可以改善思维链","type":"doc","updated":"20250920125609"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151536-708hm6r","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-708hm6r","updated":"20250920125609"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"摘要 (ABSTRACT)"}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-0hxd7up","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-0hxd7up","updated":"20250919151537"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"思维链提示 (Chain-of-thought prompting)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 与预训练"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"大型语言模型"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相结合，在复杂的推理任务上取得了令人鼓舞的成果。在本文中，我们提出了一种新的解码策略——"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"自洽性 (self-consistency)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，以取代思维链提示中使用的朴素"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"贪婪解码 (greedy decoding)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。该方法首先采样一个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"多样化的推理路径集合"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，而不仅仅是采取贪婪的那一条路径，然后通过"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"边缘化"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"掉采样的推理路径来选择"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"最一致的答案"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。自洽性利用了这样一种直觉，即一个复杂的推理问题通常允许多种不同的思维方式，但它们都会导向其"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"唯一的正确答案"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。我们广泛的实证评估表明，自洽性在包括GSM8K (+17.9%)、SVAMP (+11.0%)、AQuA (+12.2%)、StrategyQA (+6.4%) 和 ARC-challenge (+3.9%) 在内的一系列流行的算术和常识推理基准测试中，都以"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"显著的优势"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提升了思维链提示的性能。"}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-negjf0j","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"fold":"1","id":"20250919151536-negjf0j","updated":"20250919151537"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250919151536-wq30xoo","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-wq30xoo","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内容解析"}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-opsxvfo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-opsxvfo","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这篇摘要介绍了一种名为“自洽性（self-consistency）”的新技术，旨在提升大型语言模型（LLM）在复杂推理任务（如数学题和逻辑题）上的表现。"}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-wts3njw","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-wts3njw","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心问题：传统方法的局限性"}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-yjfrffe","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-yjfrffe","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151536-e2jgg9x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-e2jgg9x","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151536-n0po7xs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-n0po7xs","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"背景"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": “思维链提示”是一种让模型在给出答案前，先“思考”并写出详细推理步骤的方法。这已经证明能提高模型的准确率。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-70b9v6a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-70b9v6a","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151536-m3d7ava","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-m3d7ava","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"问题"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 传统的思维链方法通常使用“贪婪解码”。这就像一个学生做题，每一步都选择他认为最可能正确的下一步，一条路走到黑。这种方法的缺点是，如果中间某一步走错了，就很难再回到正确的轨道上，最终导致整个答案错误。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-mp0rncz","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-mp0rncz","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"解决方案：自洽性的核心思想"}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-atr87mn","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-atr87mn","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151536-67we9vr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-67we9vr","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151536-fkm8a9q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-fkm8a9q","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"类比"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": “自洽性”方法不再是只走一条路，而是像让模型“分身”成多个独立的思考者，从多个不同的角度和路径去解决同一个问题。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-0wdr4sj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-0wdr4sj","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151536-g1xrtvz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-g1xrtvz","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"具体步骤"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":":"}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-r0zkpyw","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-r0zkpyw","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151536-662uahx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-662uahx","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151536-mxyx71d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-mxyx71d","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"生成多样化路径"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 它不是只生成一个推理过程，而是生成一大堆（例如100个）不同的推理过程（即“推理路径”）。这些路径可能过程各不相同，但都是为了解决同一个问题。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-8zk7arx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-8zk7arx","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151536-kkli7un","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-kkli7un","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"投票选出最终答案"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 生成所有路径后，模型会查看这些不同路径最终得出的答案。它会选择其中出现次数最多的那个答案作为最终输出。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-yqk6ew8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-yqk6ew8","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151536-09xapvy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-09xapvy","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"基本直觉"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 这个方法背后的逻辑很简单，即“条条大路通罗马”。一个复杂的问题虽然解法多样，但正确的答案通常只有一个。如果许多种不同的思考方式都指向了同一个答案，那么这个答案正确的可能性就非常高。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-cqrm7ut","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-cqrm7ut","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"成果展示：显著的性能提升"}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-00v1gsq","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-00v1gsq","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151536-6zaid47","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-6zaid47","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151536-ig9xhqo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-ig9xhqo","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"作者通过在多个公认的测试集上进行实验，证明了“自洽性”方法的有效性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-npver05","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-npver05","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151536-zn1gs1k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-zn1gs1k","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"效果显著"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 在算术推理（GSM8K, SVAMP, AQuA）和常识推理（StrategyQA, ARC-challenge）等任务上，性能都获得了大幅提升。例如，在GSM8K这个数学题测试集上，准确率"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"惊人地提升了17.9%"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，这在人工智能领域是一个非常巨大的进步。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-6vt0lko","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-6vt0lko","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250919151536-n9g0zek","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-n9g0zek","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"综合性解析"}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-hxdejdh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-hxdejdh","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这篇摘要的核心贡献是提出了一种简单而极其有效的解码策略——"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"自洽性（self-consistency）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，用于增强大型语言模型的复杂推理能力。"}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-8cmd1v4","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-8cmd1v4","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151536-63jc99w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-63jc99w","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151536-z4uecy7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-z4uecy7","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"方法创新性"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 它巧妙地避开了传统“贪婪解码”策略的“一条路走到黑”的弊端。通过生成多样化的推理路径并进行“民主投票”，该方法极大地增强了最终答案的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"鲁棒性"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"和"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"可靠性"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。它利用了大型语言模型本身具有的生成多样性的能力，并将其转化为提高推理准确性的优势。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-v84970u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-v84970u","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151536-licw566","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-licw566","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"强大的直觉基础"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 该方法建立在一个非常符合人类解决问题直觉的原则之上：对于一个难题，如果能通过多种不同的方法都得到同一个答案，那么这个答案的可信度就极高。这使得该方法不仅效果好，而且易于理解。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-l0os2fn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-l0os2fn","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151536-my2mch9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-my2mch9","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"显著的实践价值"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 摘要中列出的一系列惊人的性能提升数据（特别是算术推理方面）强有力地证明了该方法的实用价值。这意味着，在不改变模型本身结构的情况下，仅通过改进答案的生成和选择方式，就能让现有的大型语言模型变得更“聪明”，尤其是在需要严谨逻辑推理的领域。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151536-8bas51d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151536-8bas51d","updated":"20250919151536"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总结而言，这篇论文介绍的“自洽性”方法，为如何更好地利用大型语言模型进行复杂推理提供了一个全新的、有效的视角，是“思维链”研究方向上的一个重要里程碑。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-18v1t0e","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-18v1t0e","updated":"20250920125609"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"1. 简介 (INTRODUCTION)"}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-ghbh0lm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-ghbh0lm","updated":"20250919151948"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尽管语言模型已在一系列自然语言处理（NLP）任务中展现出卓越的成功，但它们展示推理的能力通常被视为一个局限，这个问题"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"无法仅仅通过增加模型规模来解决"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" (Rae et al., 2021; BIG-bench collaboration, 2021, inter alia)。为了解决这一短板，Wei et al. (2022) 提出了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"思维链提示 (chain-of-thought prompting)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，即提示语言模型生成一系列简短的句子，以模仿一个人在解决任务时的推理过程。例如，对于问题“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"如果停车场里有3辆车，又来了2辆车，那么停车场里现在有多少辆车？"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”，语言模型会被提示回答“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"停车场里已经有3辆车。又来了2辆。现在有 3 + 2 = 5 辆车。所以答案是5。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”，而不是直接回答“5”。事实已经证明，思维链提示能够"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"显著提升模型在多步骤推理任务上的表现"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" (Wei et al., 2022)。"}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-gm58m65","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-gm58m65","updated":"20250919151948"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在本文中，我们引入一种名为"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"自洽性 (self-consistency)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的新颖解码策略，以取代思维链提示中使用的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"贪婪解码 (greedy decoding) 策略"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，从而进一步大幅提升语言模型的推理性能。自洽性利用了这样一种直觉：复杂的推理任务通常允许多种推理路径，但它们都能达到一个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"正确的答案"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" (Stanovich \u0026 West, 2000)。对于一个问题，需要越多的深思熟虑和分析，能够得出答案的推理路径的多样性就越大 (Evans, 2010)。"}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-2fzpe8f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-2fzpe8f","updated":"20250919151948"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"图1通过一个例子阐释了自洽性方法。我们首先用思维链的方式提示语言模型，但我们并"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"不贪婪地解码出最优的推理路径"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，而是提出一种“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"采样-并-边缘化"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”的解码程序：我们首先从语言模型的解码器中"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"采样"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，以生成一个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"多样化的推理路径集合"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"；每条推理路径都可能导向一个最终答案，然后我们通过"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"边缘化"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"掉所有采样的推理路径来确定最优答案，从而在最终答案集合中找到"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"最一致的答案"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这种方法类似于人类的经验：如果多种不同的思维方式都导向同一个答案，那么人们对这个最终答案是正确的就会有更大的信心。与其他解码方法相比，自洽性"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"避免了困扰贪婪解码的重复性和局部最优性"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，同时"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"减轻了单一采样生成所带来的随机性"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-2kd7803","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"fold":"1","id":"20250919151947-2kd7803","updated":"20250919151948"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250919151947-7qei0ze","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-7qei0ze","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内容解析"}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-rh329e7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-rh329e7","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这部分内容为论文的核心思想奠定了基础，清晰地阐述了研究背景、现有方法的局限性以及本文提出的创新点。"}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-cxog27g","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-cxog27g","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"问题背景：推理是LLM的短板"}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-t43xxok","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-t43xxok","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-6w7hv50","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-6w7hv50","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-ot39w5x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-ot39w5x","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"作者首先指出，尽管大型语言模型（LLM）在很多任务上很成功，但"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"逻辑推理"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是它们的“阿喀琉斯之踵”。简单地把模型做得更大并不能完全解决这个问题。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-2x0t3tv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-2x0t3tv","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-i23srtu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-i23srtu","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"现有方案"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 为了提升推理能力，研究者提出了“思维链提示”（Chain-of-Thought, CoT）。这种方法不是让模型直接给出答案，而是引导它像人一样，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"一步一步地写出思考过程"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。事实证明，这种“慢思考”的方式确实能有效提高模型解决复杂问题的能力。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-bhhp2us","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-bhhp2us","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"现有方案的缺陷：贪婪解码的风险"}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-fbkx8f3","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-fbkx8f3","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-yaavwew","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-yaavwew","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-etk91jz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-etk91jz","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"传统的思维链提示采用的是“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"贪婪解码"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”。这可以理解为一种“一条路走到黑”的策略。在生成推理过程的每一步，模型都会选择它认为"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"当前最可能正确的下一步"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-109tlad","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-109tlad","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-2mdukap","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-2mdukap","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"风险在于"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：这种策略非常短视。如果在推理的早期步骤中出现了一个微小的错误，整个后续的推理链条就会偏离轨道，导致最终结果功亏一篑。它很容易陷入“局部最优”的陷阱。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-ho5maus","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-ho5maus","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心创新：自洽性 (Self-Consistency)"}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-lroqdki","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-lroqdki","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-cjyqhsi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-cjyqhsi","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-wc2ccdd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-wc2ccdd","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心思想"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 作者提出的“自洽性”方法，其灵感来源于一个简单的生活常识——“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"条条大路通罗马"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”。一个复杂问题可能有多种解法，但正确的答案通常是唯一的。如果多种不同的思考方式都指向了同一个答案，那么这个答案正确的概率就非常高。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-1js7w7y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-1js7w7y","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-zd1bl0y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-zd1bl0y","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"“采样-并-边缘化”流程"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":":"}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-r1t349h","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-r1t349h","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-r9xs4ga","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-r9xs4ga","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-fr3fq78","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-fr3fq78","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"采样 (Sample)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 不再只走一条路，而是让模型发散思维，生成"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"许多条（多样化的）不同的推理路径"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-ukt0tv4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-ukt0tv4","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-wu4tn7a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-wu4tn7a","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"边缘化 (Marginalize)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 忽略掉具体的推理过程（即“边缘化”掉路径），只看每条路径最终得出的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"答案"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-gc5bv3f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-gc5bv3f","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-9euvzjn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-9euvzjn","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"投票 (Vote)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 在所有最终答案中，进行一次“民主投票”，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"选择出现次数最多的那个作为最终答案"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-eddq49s","Type"