PaLM-540B (Chowdhery et al., 2022)。在所有四个语言模型上，自洽性都以"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"惊人的优势"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"改进了思维链提示的性能。特别是，当与PaLM-540B或GPT-3结合使用时，自洽性在多个流行的算术推理任务上"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"达到了新的SOTA（业界最佳）性能"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，包括GSM8K (Cobbe et al., 2021)（+17.9%的绝对准确率提升），SVAMP (Patel et al., 2021)（+11.0%），AQuA (Ling et al., 2017)（+12.2%），以及跨常识推理任务的StrategyQA (Geva et al., 2021)（+6.4%）和ARC-challenge (Clark et al., 2018)（+3.9%）。在额外的实验中，我们展示了自洽性可以在添加思维链提示可能损害性能的NLP任务上，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"稳健地提升性能"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" (Ye \u0026 Durrett, 2022)。我们还展示了自洽性显著优于样本和排序（sample-and-rank）、束搜索（beam search）、基于集成的（ensemble-based）方法，并且对采样策略和不完美的提示具有"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"鲁棒性"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-m6qxlkz","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"fold":"1","id":"20250919151947-m6qxlkz","updated":"20250919151948"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250919151947-3msf0fp","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-3msf0fp","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内容解析"}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-7e40fwm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-7e40fwm","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这部分详细阐述了自洽性方法的关键优势和其惊人的实验效果，强调了其普适性和高效性。"}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-irjunct","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-irjunct","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心优势：简单、通用、高效"}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-1esd9jr","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-1esd9jr","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-neymxe4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-neymxe4","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-mfblmjc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-mfblmjc","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"完全无监督"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 这是该方法最大的优点之一。它"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"不需要任何额外的人工标注数据"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这意味着它成本低廉，易于部署。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-j8vnp63","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-j8vnp63","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-0p1tf6v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-0p1tf6v","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"即插即用"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 它适用于"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"任何现成的、已经预训练好的大型语言模型"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，无需对模型本身进行任何修改、微调或额外训练。这与那些需要训练一个“验证器”或“重排器”的复杂方法形成了鲜明对比。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-qrludpm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-qrludpm","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-fusybm6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-fusybm6","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"自集成 (Self-Ensemble)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 传统上，为了提升性能，人们会训练好几个不同的模型（集成），然后综合它们的预测。这种方法成本高昂。自洽性巧妙地在"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"一个模型内部实现了类似的效果"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，让模型自己与自己“商议”，因此被称为“自集成”，性价比极高。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-lwl35v0","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-lwl35v0","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"惊人的实验结果"}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-dhvhglx","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-dhvhglx","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-myz4aqg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-myz4aqg","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-5lziv2e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-5lziv2e","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"普适性强"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 作者在"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"四种不同的大型语言模型"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（从200亿到5400亿参数）上都进行了测试，结果表明自洽性在所有模型上都取得了显著的效果，证明了其方法的普适性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-5t8tkps","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-5t8tkps","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-3earo1c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-3earo1c","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"性能提升巨大"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 在多个公认的推理任务基准上，自洽性带来了“惊人的”性能提升。尤其是在数学推理任务GSM8K上，准确率"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"直接提升了17.9%"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，这是一个非常巨大的飞跃，足以将一个表现平平的模型提升到业界顶尖水平（SOTA）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-rjm8rql","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-rjm8rql","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-pqdw690","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-pqdw690","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"鲁棒性好"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 该方法不仅在标准任务上表现优异，还能在一些特殊情况下（例如思维链提示本身效果不佳的任务）稳定地提升性能。此外，它对不同的采样策略和不够完美的提示（prompt）也不敏感，显示出很强的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"鲁棒性"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-ronsqbz","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"fold":"1","id":"20250919151947-ronsqbz","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250919151947-jkxojh3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-jkxojh3","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"综合性解析"}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-4fpr0ww","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-4fpr0ww","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本文的引言部分清晰地构建了一个“问题-方案-验证”的逻辑链条，旨在向读者全面介绍“自洽性”这一创新方法。"}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-h6i7k5f","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-h6i7k5f","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-fqbsxqt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-fqbsxqt","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-f428y6z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-f428y6z","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"靶向明确的问题"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 文章开篇即点明了大型语言模型的核心短板——"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"复杂推理能力不足"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，并指出现有的“思维链提示”虽然有效，但其依赖的“贪婪解码”策略存在"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"固有的脆弱性"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，容易“一步错，步步错”。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-9k9go9i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-9k9go9i","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-5gibhua","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-5gibhua","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提出优雅的解决方案"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 针对这一问题，文章提出了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"自洽性 (Self-Consistency)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。该方案的核心思想源于“条条大路通罗马”的直觉，通过“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"采样多种推理路径，投票选出最一致答案"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”的机制，用“集体智慧”弥补了单一路径的不足。如图1所示，这种方法能够有效地过滤掉因逻辑或计算错误导致的异常答案，从而选出正确的最终结果。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-imdp7s7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-imdp7s7","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-tgk9a3a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-tgk9a3a","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"强调方案的优越性"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 文章着重强调了自洽性方法的几大优点：它"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"完全无监督"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"、"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"无需额外训练或数据"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，并且可以"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"即插即用"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"于任何现有的语言模型。它是一种“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"自集成"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”技术，用极低的边际成本实现了传统上需要多个模型才能达到的集成效果，兼具高效与经济。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-w482q17","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-w482q17","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919151947-ppcq0n8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-ppcq0n8","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"展示强大的实验支撑"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 最后，文章用一系列令人信服的实验数据来佐证其方法的有效性。自洽性不仅在多种模型、多种任务上都取得了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"显著甚至破纪录的性能提升"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（尤其是在数学推理上），而且表现出了很强的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"鲁棒性"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，证明了其广泛的适用价值。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919151947-syqelxn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919151947-syqelxn","updated":"20250919151947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总结来说，这篇引言成功地将“自洽性”塑造为一个简单、直观、却又极其强大的技术。它不是去重新设计一个更复杂的模型，而是通过一种更聪明的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"解码策略"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，极大地释放了现有大型语言模型内在的推理潜力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-eordj55","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-eordj55","updated":"20250920125609"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"2. 基于多样化推理路径的自洽性 (SELF-CONSISTENCY OVER DIVERSE REASONING PATHS)"}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-hpp0340","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-hpp0340","updated":"20250919152518"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人类的一个显著特点是人们的思维方式各不相同。很自然地可以推断，在需要深思熟虑的任务中，很可能有多种方法来解决问题。我们提出，这一过程可以通过从语言模型的解码器中"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"进行采样"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"来在语言模型中进行模拟。例如，如图1所示，一个模型可以对一个数学问题生成多个看似合理的回答，而这些回答都得出了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"同一个正确的答案"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（输出1和3）。由于语言模型并非完美的推理者，模型也可能产生错误的推理路径或在某个推理步骤中出错（例如，在输出2中），但这类解答"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"不太可能得出相同的答案"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。也就是说，我们假设，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"正确的推理过程，即使它们是多样的，其最终答案的一致性也倾向于比错误的推理过程更高"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-fhwlvdb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-fhwlvdb","updated":"20250919152518"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们利用这一直觉提出了以下的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"自洽性方法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。首先，用一组人工编写的思维链范例来提示语言模型 (Wei et al., 2022)。接下来，我们从语言模型的解码器中采样，生成一个由多个候选推理路径组成的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"多样化集合"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。自洽性与现有的采样算法兼容，包括温度采样 (Ackley et al., 1985; Fickler \u0026 Goldberg, 2017)、top-k采样 (Fan et al., 2018; Holtzman et al., 2018; Radford et al., 2019) 和 nucleus采样 (Holtzman et al., 2020)。最后，我们通过"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"边缘化"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"掉采样的推理路径，并选择在生成的答案中"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"最一致"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的那个答案来聚合最终答案。"}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-urzgkl9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-urzgkl9","updated":"20250920125355"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"更具体地说，假设生成的候选答案 aᵢ 来自于一个最终答案集合 A，其中 i = 1, ..., m 表示第 m 个候选输出。给定一个提示（prompt）和一个问题（question），自洽性引入了一个额外的隐变量 rᵢ，它是一个代表第 i 个输出中推理路径的token序列，然后将 (rᵢ, aᵢ) 的生成过程耦合起来，其中 rᵢ → aᵢ，即推理路径 rᵢ 是可选的，并且仅用于得出最终答案 aᵢ。例如，在图1的输出3中，前几句话“她早餐吃了3个……所以她赚了9个蛋 * "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"2 = "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18”构成了 rᵢ，而答案18则来自最后一句话“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"答案是$18"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”，并被解析出来。在从模型的解码器中采样了多个 (rᵢ, aᵢ) 对之后，自洽性通过在最终答案集上进行"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"多数投票"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"来应用聚合步骤，即 arg maxₐ Σᵢ=₁ᵐ 𝟙(aᵢ = a)，或者我们所定义的最终答案集中的“最一致”的答案。"}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-o3ed63o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-o3ed63o","updated":"20250919152518"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在表1中，我们通过使用不同的答案聚合策略，测试了在一系列推理任务上的准确率。在聚合答案时，可以对每个 (rᵢ, aᵢ) 根据其概率 P(rᵢ, aᵢ | prompt, question) 进行加权，也可以不加权。需要注意的是，要计算 P(rᵢ, aᵢ | prompt, question)，我们可以采用 (rᵢ, aᵢ) 中所有token的未归一化概率，给定 (prompt, question)，也可以采用 Brown et al. (2020) 建议的归一化条件概率。"}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-4rclhmv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-4rclhmv","updated":"20250920125609"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"公式 (1): "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"P(rᵢ, aᵢ | prompt, question) = exp({1\\over K} Σ_{k=1}ᴷ log P(tₖ | prompt, question, t₁, ..., tₖ₋₁))"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n"}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-7qepeda","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-7qepeda","updated":"20250919152518"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其中 P(tₖ | prompt, question, t₁, ..., tₖ₋₁) 是在给定 prompt、question 和之前的 token t₁,...,tₖ₋₁ 的条件下，第 k 个 token tₖ 的对数概率，K 是 (rᵢ, aᵢ) 中的 token 总数。在表1中，我们展示了“未加权求和”与简单的多数投票效果相当，而“归一化加权求和”的准确率也与之类似。² 此外，归一化条件概率 P(rᵢ, aᵢ | prompt, question) 对于每个 (rᵢ, aᵢ) 都相当接近，即语言模型认为这些生成的输出具有相似的可能性。² 此外，当聚合答案时，如表1所示，“归一化加权求和”（公式1）与其未归一化的对应项相比，产生了更高的准确率。在表1中，我们还报告了“加权平均”的结果，即每个 aᵢ 的权重为其归一化权重除以 Σᵢ=₁ᵐ 𝟙(aᵢ = a)，这种方法表现更差。"}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-v40hrgi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-v40hrgi","updated":"20250919152518"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自洽性探索了开放式文本生成和需要固定答案的最优文本生成之间的有趣空间。推理任务通常需要固定答案，这就是为什么研究人员通常使用贪婪解码的原因 (Radford et al., 2019; Wei et al., 2022; Chowdhery et al., 2022)。然而，即使答案是固定的，引入推理过程的多样性也可能非常有益；因此我们利用了常用于开放式文本生成的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"采样"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方法 (Radford et al., 2019; Brown et al., 2020; Thoppilan et al., 2022) 来实现这一目标。需要注意的是，自洽性只能应用于最终答案来自"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"固定答案集"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的问题，但原则上，如果能在多个生成结果之间定义一个好的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"一致性度量标准"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（例如，两个答案是否一致或矛盾），这种方法也可以扩展到开放式文本生成问题。"}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-6822ivt","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-6822ivt","updated":"20250919152518"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250919152517-9cgy8v6","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-9cgy8v6","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内容解析"}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-ovemkab","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-ovemkab","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这一部分深入阐述了“自洽性”方法的理论基础、具体实现方式和适用范围。"}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-2x5n965","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-2x5n965","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"理论基础：模拟人类思维多样性"}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-mwcylg4","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-mwcylg4","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919152517-64fsuaa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-64fsuaa","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919152517-anh7vbd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-anh7vbd","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心假设"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 作者将方法的根基建立在一个深刻的洞察上："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"正确的思维路径是多样的，但它们殊途同归；而错误的思维路径则千奇百怪，且很少会碰巧得出同一个错误答案。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-8w9y80h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-8w9y80h","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919152517-h4raunc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-h4raunc","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"模拟方式"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 他们提出，可以通过语言模型的“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"采样 (sampling)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”功能来模拟这种思维的多样性。采样允许模型在生成文本时引入一定的随机性，从而产生多种不同的推理过程，而不是像“贪婪解码”那样只生成一条最可能的路径。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-3j9utw3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-3j9utw3","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"具体实现步骤"}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-af8d4fi","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-af8d4fi","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919152517-4gvvhqc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-4gvvhqc","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919152517-a1v9ooh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-a1v9ooh","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示 (Prompt)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 和标准的思维链（CoT）一样，首先给模型一些包含解题步骤的例子。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-3r8x4lw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-3r8x4lw","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919152517-4mzhwx7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-4mzhwx7","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"多样化采样 (Sample)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 这是核心步骤。使用温度采样（temperature sampling）或top-k采样等技术，从模型的解码器中生成"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"一大批"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（例如100个）候选的“推理路径 + 最终答案”对，即 (rᵢ, aᵢ)。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-cfobncj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-cfobncj","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919152517-y85vi55","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-y85vi55","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"聚合与决策 (Aggregate)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 这是最后一步，也是最简单的一步。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"忽略掉所有的推理过程 (rᵢ)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，只看最终的答案 (aᵢ)。然后进行"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"多数投票（majority vote）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，选择出现次数最多的那个答案作为最终输出。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-yr5e4je","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-yr5e4je","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"方法的扩展与局限"}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-w5k2frb","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-w5k2frb","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919152517-h8aeq82","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-h8aeq82","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919152517-fbizk2a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-fbizk2a","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"加权投票的探索"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 作者还探索了更复杂的聚合方式，比如根据每个推理路径的“置信度”（即模型生成该路径的概率）来给投票加权。但从后面的表格数据可以看出，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"简单的多数投票效果已经非常好"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，复杂的加权方案并没有带来显著提升。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-e9bspia","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-e9bspia","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919152517-4wuzp0v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-4wuzp0v","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"适用范围"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 目前，自洽性最适用于那些"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"答案是固定的、明确的"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"问题（如数学题、选择题）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919152517-u7b0h5v","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919152517-u7b0h5v","updated":"20250919152517"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919152517-ur0vbz8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properti