"20250919153022-ok18bzu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919153022-ok18bzu","updated":"20250919153022"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919153022-1pc1law","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919153022-1pc1law","updated":"20250919153022"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"PaLM-540B (Chowdhery et al., 2022)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是一个稠密的、从左到右的、仅解码器的语言模型，拥有5400亿参数，在一个包含网页、书籍、维基百科、新闻文章、源代码和社交媒体对话的高质量语料库上进行了预训练。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919153022-ryxw5sn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919153022-ryxw5sn","updated":"20250919153023"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们在所有实验中都采用"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"少样本设置"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，没有进行训练或微调。为了公平比较，我们使用了与Wei et al. (2022) 相同的提示：对于所有算术推理任务，我们使用相同的8个手动编写的范例；对于每个常识推理任务，从训练集中随机抽取4-7个范例，并与手动编写的思维链提示相结合。⁶ 提示中使用的完整细节见附录A.3。"}]},{"ID":"20250919153022-zh6dt5t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919153022-zh6dt5t","updated":"20250919153023"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"采样方案"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。为了对多样化的推理路径进行采样，我们遵循了类似于Radford et al. (2019); Holtzman et al. (2020) 中用于开放式文本生成的设置。具体来说，对于UL2-20B和LaMDA-137B，我们应用了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"温度 T = 0.5"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 并截断了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"top-k = 40"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的词汇。对于PaLM-540B，我们应用了 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"T = 0.7, k = 40"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，对于GPT-3，我们使用了 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"T = 0.7"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 且没有top-k截断。我们在第3.5节提供了一项消融研究，以显示自洽性通常对采样策略和参数具有"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"鲁棒性"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20250919153022